Wano</b>

412
00:31:13.100 --> 00:31:17.770
Wano's letter-arrows
can travel a great distance.

413
00:31:25.070 --> 00:31:26.320
You guys...

414
00:31:27.950 --> 00:31:32.450
If I somehow manage to survive this...

415
00:31:32.450 --> 00:31:34.580
I will...

416
00:31:34.580 --> 00:31:38.170
open the country!

417
00:31:41.380 --> 00:31:44.220
What's he babbling about?

418
00:31:44.220 --> 00:31:48.890
You spoke of opening
the borders before, Lord Oden.

419
00:31:48.890 --> 00:31:54.270
You said that the Kozuki Clan had
something to do with our isolation.

420
00:31:54.730 --> 00:32:00.360
What did you learn out there
while traveling with Roger's crew?!

421
00:32:02.980 --> 00:32:08.530
Long ago, this country was
closed off from the outside world...

422
00:32:08.530 --> 00:32:10.530
by the Kozuki Clan!

423
00:32:13.080 --> 00:32:18.960
It was done to protect Wano
from a great threat!

424
00:32:18.960 --> 00:32:21.210
Wano...

425
00:32:21.210 --> 00:32:23.460
No, the entire world...

426
00:32:23.460 --> 00:32:26.670
awaits a certain figure!

427
00:32:28.050 --> 00:32:38.940
After 800 years of waiting, our nation
must be ready to welcome and aid them!

428
00:32:41.860 --> 00:32:43.360
I will be blunt.

429
00:32:49.530 --> 00:32:52.030
They are going...

430
00:32:52.830 --> 00:32:55.870
to kill me today!

431
00:32:57.870 --> 00:32:59.620
No!

432
00:32:59.620 --> 00:33:02.500
But you can still survive this!

433
00:33:03.210 --> 00:33:05.590
You are already a third of the way through!

434
00:33:06.130 --> 00:33:08.670
I want you to...

435
00:33:09.720 --> 00:33:13.550
open Wano in my stead!

436
00:33:14.600 --> 00:33:17.060
We can do it togeth–

437
00:33:18.520 --> 00:33:22.360
Your dream is our dream!

438
00:33:25.110 --> 00:33:27.820
Well said!

439
00:33:31.450 --> 00:33:33.820
Thirty minutes to go!

440
00:33:36.240 --> 00:33:40.920
By this point, even the
heat haze was a lethal hell.

441
00:33:40.920 --> 00:33:43.710
The boiling oil was cooking Oden alive.

442
00:33:45.920 --> 00:33:48.510
Why isn't he dead yet?!

443
00:33:48.510 --> 00:33:51.470
Raise the temperature!

444
00:33:59.850 --> 00:34:01.270
Ten minutes to go!

445
00:34:05.690 --> 00:34:09.400
Is he impervious to heat?!

446
00:34:11.030 --> 00:34:12.410
Five minutes to go!

447
00:34:15.660 --> 00:34:17.290
One minute to go!

448
00:34:19.830 --> 00:34:20.660
Ten seconds!

449
00:34:23.870 --> 00:34:25.000
Three seconds!

450
00:34:32.170 --> 00:34:33.260
One second!

451
00:34:39.810 --> 00:34:44.400
He did it!

452
00:34:44.400 --> 00:34:46.770
It's a miracle!

453
00:34:46.770 --> 00:34:50.230
He overcame the execution!

454
00:34:51.110 --> 00:34:52.320
Lord Oden...

455
00:34:52.320 --> 00:34:55.700
He withstood the boiling!

456
00:34:57.030 --> 00:34:58.410
He did it!

457
00:34:59.120 --> 00:35:01.790
Lord Oden won!

458
00:35:01.790 --> 00:35:04.210
His name has been cleared too!

459
00:35:04.210 --> 00:35:08.500
The whole country is on our side once more!

460
00:35:08.500 --> 00:35:11.170
You're in for it now, Kaido!

461
00:35:11.170 --> 00:35:13.300
Don't antagonize him, you stupid cat!

462
00:35:13.300 --> 00:35:15.680
Why not? We've won!

463
00:35:23.980 --> 00:35:29.570
I amended the execution method
to death by firing squad a minute ago!

464
00:35:30.860 --> 00:35:34.280
And we'll execute not only Oden...

465
00:35:34.280 --> 00:35:37.200
but his entire family as well!

466
00:35:40.870 --> 00:35:43.200
You petty child!

467
00:35:43.200 --> 00:35:44.620
That wasn't the deal!

468
00:35:44.620 --> 00:35:45.620
Lord Oden–

469
00:35:52.340 --> 00:35:54.550
If anyone's got a problem, speak up!

470
00:35:54.550 --> 00:35:57.130
We'll fill you with lead!

471
00:36:03.770 --> 00:36:06.690
I'm counting on you guys!

472
00:36:08.850 --> 00:36:13.690
Open Wano's borders!

473
00:36:33.250 --> 00:36:35.090
Run!

474
00:36:35.090 --> 00:36:37.050
To Kuri!

475
00:36:39.970 --> 00:36:40.890
Shinobu!

476
00:36:46.680 --> 00:36:49.480
Do not look back!

477
00:36:54.630 --> 00:36:56.110
– Kozuki Oden!
– Kozuki Oden!

478
00:36:57.450 --> 00:37:00.990
That was quite a story.

479
00:37:00.990 --> 00:37:02.780
Lord Oden!

480
00:37:03.160 --> 00:37:05.830
Kill them all!

481
00:37:10.210 --> 00:37:11.920
Go after them!

482
00:37:11.920 --> 00:37:15.130
Leave no trace of the Kozuki name!

483
00:37:16.340 --> 00:37:20.630
It seems your body is as
good as "dead" anyway...

484
00:37:20.630 --> 00:37:24.850
The least I can do is put you down!

485
00:37:26.850 --> 00:37:30.390
The Kozuki era ends here!

486
00:37:30.390 --> 00:37:32.940
You're all gonna die!

487
00:37:34.980 --> 00:37:38.320
Do not underestimate my samurai!

488
00:37:42.240 --> 00:37:43.320
Lord Oden!

489
00:37:45.370 --> 00:37:46.540
Stop eating, you brats!

490
00:37:47.450 --> 00:37:49.120
I said stop!

491
00:37:49.120 --> 00:37:50.370
Do not give him any more!

492
00:38:02.840 --> 00:38:04.970
Whoa! I give up! I give up! I give up!

493
00:38:04.970 --> 00:38:06.510
I thought you were a corpse!

494
00:38:18.030 --> 00:38:20.650
Lord Oden!

495
00:38:27.660 --> 00:38:30.830
How can an ass who grew up
pampered in the capital...

496
00:38:31.410 --> 00:38:34.670
understand what it's like to live in hell?!

497
00:38:34.670 --> 00:38:38.250
Is that all you really want to say?!

498
00:38:47.140 --> 00:38:49.680
You should all be ashamed!

499
00:38:50.020 --> 00:38:52.980
It is pathetic to torment such little creatures!

500
00:38:58.070 --> 00:39:00.030
I am hungry...

501
00:39:00.360 --> 00:39:02.990
Because you keep lending money!

502
00:39:12.330 --> 00:39:13.290
All right!

503
00:39:13.750 --> 00:39:16.290
Go steal some grub!

504
00:39:16.290 --> 00:39:18.250
A daimyo should not say that!

505
00:39:24.970 --> 00:39:29.010
It doesn't matter if your life
has become a pitiful mess.

506
00:39:29.010 --> 00:39:33.230
People will remember your
heroic death for generations.

507
00:39:33.230 --> 00:39:35.900
They can forget me...

508
00:39:37.690 --> 00:39:40.270
for all I care...

509
00:39:40.270 --> 00:39:41.440
but...

510
00:39:46.410 --> 00:39:50.830
my spirit will live on!

511
00:39:51.410 --> 00:39:54.580
Sorry about the old hag.

512
00:39:54.580 --> 00:39:57.250
I saw to her death myself.

513
00:39:57.250 --> 00:39:59.290
You did?

514
00:39:59.670 --> 00:40:01.210
How upright of you.

515
00:40:01.960 --> 00:40:04.840
Build your strength while you can!

516
00:40:07.680 --> 00:40:09.760
I am content...

517
00:40:09.970 --> 00:40:15.930
<b>I am content
to become
a story to be
shared over drinks</b>

518
00:40:10.970 --> 00:40:15.930
to become a story
to be shared over drinks...

519
00:40:18.560 --> 00:40:20.690
My loyal samurai!

520
00:40:21.480 --> 00:40:22.480
Toki!

521
00:40:23.110 --> 00:40:24.490
Momonosuke!

522
00:40:24.490 --> 00:40:25.860
Hiyori!

523
00:40:31.910 --> 00:40:34.240
I am going on ahead!

524
00:40:41.040 --> 00:40:44.590
Oden was meant...

525
00:40:44.380 --> 00:40:46.050
<b>Oden was meant</b>

526
00:41:15.740 --> 00:41:19.920
<b>to boil</b>
– ...to boil!
– ...to boil!

527
00:41:37.180 --> 00:41:45.070
One legend has ended, and the new legend will
be passed down to the stars of the next stage.
